{"tid":1906222,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【疫情爆發】傳因劇情與「新冠肺炎」相似 Marvel改劇本重拍","createTime":"2020-03-01T19:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T12:21:25.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"80dfc970393bed9e392327b8adf0f44b2fe7c292","tid":1906222,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:07:45.000Z","msg":"Marvel影集《The Falcon and The Winter Soldier》由安東尼麥基（Anthony Mackie）及施巴斯坦史丹（Sebastian Stan）主演，影集將於今年8月開播。不過有外國傳媒報道，由於劇情跟「新冠肺炎」相似，因此重寫劇本兼重拍！<br />\n<br />\n其實Mavrel也不是第一次通過重新拍攝或改寫劇本，據《Murphy&rsquo;s Multiverse》的文章，Marvel首個迪士尼迷你系列《The Falcon and The Winter Soldier》，正是因為改寫劇情而延長了拍攝時間。<br />\n報道指，劇情講述一種在全球傳播的可怕流行病毒，與目前的「新冠肺炎」相似，太過於接近現實。Mavrel擔心到8月開播時，仍引起觀眾不安，加上迪士尼跟中國的關係，所以臨時決定重寫兼重拍該部分。"},{"pid":"49a688313caca6c0732283fd8f12f4f6871880fc","tid":1906222,"uid":54946,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:09:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母Disney"},{"pid":"cc9b21abec36b6a6d3654656828eeca8d80eca89","tid":1906222,"uid":1024,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 迪士尼跟中國的關係，所以臨時決定重寫兼重拍該部分。 </span>"},{"pid":"ad04f127044a234fd1bf5b4397a8b03ad50d5e2f","tid":1906222,"uid":123774,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係武漢肺炎</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"be2373748c88db32da6128a0ea854cb1996e5a29","tid":1906222,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad04f127044a234fd1bf5b4397a8b03ad50d5e2f","tid":1906222,"uid":123774,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係武漢肺炎</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree